  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-12-13",
  "religion": "Leone was raised a Sikh and still seems to adhere to a qualified version of that faith.",
  "politicalViews": "Leone appears to be a Democrat, though she isn't afraid of criticizing Obama.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Sunny Leone, whose real name is Karenjit Kaur Vohra, was born in Sarnia, Ontario, Canada and grew up there, in Fort Gratiot, Michigan and in Lake Forest, California."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Leone's parents immigrated from India and she was raised in a Sikh household.",
      "sourceTitle": "Pornstar Sunny Leone on thriving in the wild, wild west of the adult film industry",
      "sourceUrl": "http://cltampa.com/dailyloaf/archives/2010/08/23/pornstar-sunny-leone-on-thriving-in-the-wild-wild-west-of-the-adult-industry-nsfw#.ULcCNYXJCBg"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " Of the religion of her heritage, she said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 4,
      "parentId": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "You walk into a temple and you're greeted with the utmost respect. You're completely equal to your peers. Everyone helps everybody. You do community work; you help your neighbor. But, just like any religion it doesn't want you to shoot adult material. I mean, I grew up going to temple every Sunday.",
      "sourceTitle": "Pornstar Sunny Leone on thriving in the wild, wild west of the adult film industry",
      "sourceUrl": "http://cltampa.com/dailyloaf/archives/2010/08/23/pornstar-sunny-leone-on-thriving-in-the-wild-wild-west-of-the-adult-industry-nsfw#.ULcCNYXJCBg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "But in an effort to integrate her into western society, Leone's parents sent her to Catholic school in Canada.",
      "sourceTitle": "Pornstar Sunny Leone on thriving in the wild, wild west of the adult film industry",
      "sourceUrl": "http://cltampa.com/dailyloaf/archives/2010/08/23/pornstar-sunny-leone-on-thriving-in-the-wild-wild-west-of-the-adult-industry-nsfw#.ULcCNYXJCBg"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " She does, however, try to stick to her Sikh roots to some degree",
      "sourceTitle": "Sunny Leone's America",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20110710213113/http://www.eyeweekly.com/scrollingeye/article/32910"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " and maintains a sense of spirituality, but Leone doesn't think it necessarily conflicts with her career choice and won't let it get in the way of her work. She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 7,
      "parentId": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Girls will leave the industry claiming that they found God. Well, the fact is, God has always been with them the entire time.",
      "sourceTitle": "Sunny Leone's America",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20110710213113/http://www.eyeweekly.com/scrollingeye/article/32910"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 9,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Porn and politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 10
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Leone, a dual Canadian-American citizen,",
      "sourceTitle": "Ambush Interview #97",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.ambushinterview.com/97/interview97.html"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " appears to be politically aware. She has said she has a crush on Obama.",
      "sourceTitle": "Sunny Leone's America",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20110710213113/http://www.eyeweekly.com/scrollingeye/article/32910"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " Maybe that's the equivalent of a porn star endorsement. But she did declare that she would vote for him in 2008 during \"Declare Yourself's\" get-out-the-vote campaign.",
      "sourceTitle": "Sunny Leone's America",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20110710213113/http://www.eyeweekly.com/scrollingeye/article/32910"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "She further clarified her position during a condemnation of George W. Bush:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 13,
      "parentId": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "George W. Bush hasn't been very good for the adult industry. Plus, when we're paying $5 a gallon for gas, it means that it's time for a real change.",
      "sourceTitle": "Sunny Leone's America",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20110710213113/http://www.eyeweekly.com/scrollingeye/article/32910"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 14
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "But the honeymoon appeared to be over when, three years into the Obama administration, Leone tweeted:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 16,
      "parentId": 15
    },
    {
      "parentId": 16,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Pres Obama's tax plan sucks balls.",
      "sourceTitle": "SunnyLeone: Pres Obama's tax plan sucks balls",
      "sourceUrl": "https://twitter.com/SunnyLeone/status/115824264476766209"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 17
    },
    {
      "parentId": 17,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "No word on if she went with Romney in 2012, but it seems doubtful."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 18
    },
    {
      "parentId": 18,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "One last interesting political note. First off, the reputable news source, Reuters, reported that late terrorist Osama bin Laden was a porn fan and stacks of sexually explicit videos were found during raids of his former hideouts.",
      "sourceTitle": "Exclusive: Pornography found in bin Laden hideout: officials",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/13/us-binladen-porn-idUSTRE74C4RK20110513"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 18,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " Rumor has it, when he was shot dead by U.S. special forces in northern Pakistan in 2011, a Sunny Leone video was either playing or on the premises.",
      "sourceTitle": "Was Osama killed while watching Sunny Leone's steamy video?",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.emirates247.com/bollywood/take-one/was-osama-killed-while-watching-sunny-leone-s-steamy-video-2012-07-09-1.466473"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 19
    },
    {
      "parentId": 19,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "That is all."
    }
  ],
